(2047, 0, '2022-11-03', 'AvailableCar Cannock', '', 1, 0, '[\"Ash\",\"Jordan\",\"\",\"\"]', 'Available car cannock WiFi changeover day - same as Donington and Sutton with regards to setting up the new WiFi on devices essential to business operations. \n\nSet up 3 new PC\'s and 3 Monitors in new pod behind reception. Couldn\'t leave them running as no power had been ran. PC\'s left in place awaiting electricians to get AC Power to them. They\'re all on domain so ready to plug & play as we set them up in server room.\n\nAlso set up 8 monitors for the admin staff.\n\nRemoved Dratytek AP from workshop and replaced with 5port switch. Also added an extra 5 port switch in server room to allow for the customer wifi VLAN to be hardwired to the totems in showroom and ensure they were off the normal LAN.\n\nMONITOR SERVICE TAGS:\n7KWY1R3, GP8CQP3, DC9CQP3, F667QP3, 5M8CQP3, 4J7C8N3, 178CQP3, 1X77QP3, 2B77QP3, 3W8CQP3, 2N67QP3', '[\"27.00\",\"23.90\",\"0.00\",\"0.00\",\"0.00\"]', '[[\"Dell Optiplex 3090 (SFF Tower)\",\"71gmfr3\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"Dell Optiplex 3090 (SFF Tower)\",\"9mfmfr3\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"Dell Optiplex 3090 (SFF Tower)\",\"135kfr3\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"NETGEAR GS105UK\",\"3TL1215T04A8\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"NETGEAR GS105UK\",\"3TL1215X03874\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"DELL P2422H (QUANTITY: 11)\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"]]', 0);
