(2048, 0, '2022-11-04', 'AvailableCar Leeds', '', 1, 0, '[\"Ash\",\"George\",\"\",\"\"]', 'Final visit to handle the last site on the Available car WiFi project. Got as many devices as was given to us/found by us onto the new secured WiFi network.\n\nRemoved a Draytek AP from workshop and also disabled an additional one on the custy toilet roof to ensure that no non whitelisted WiFi was being broadcast.', '[\"45.00\",\"13.88\",\"0.00\",\"0.00\",\"0.00\"]', '[[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"]]', 0),
(2049, 0, '2022-11-07', 'ArenaUK', '', 0, 6, '[\"Ash\",\"Dean\\n\",\"\",\"\"]', 'Early AM trip to ArenaUK to investigate phone issues and complaints regarding WiFi speeds and an outage in the Glebe Farm rental house.\n\nThe phones is an issue to do with the phone system which old IT Guy James knows about and will resolve. Should be eradicated when Emtel swap the phones to the new Yealink system.\n\nThe slow WiFi in the main office is down to the uplink. The AP is fed by a switch which is connected to a 100mb link. Not much we can do with that until the Fibre run is operational.\n\nThe Glebe farmhouse issue was found to be an unplugged PtP link. When the link was restored I was able to re-adopt 2 extra AP\'s and get the new WiFi network broadcasting over there too.\n\nAlso spent time investigating a CCTV camera being down, seemed to be a cable issue related to using seemingly indoor rated cable outdoors. Have relayed to Simon to ease his troubleshooting down the line.\n\nAlso found another damaged PtP link which is unable to be resolved as the station appears to be damaged. Will reuse equipment replaced by Fibre link to get this connection working again as it won\'t be worth running cable to it.', '[\"18.00\",\"0.00\",\"0.00\",\"0.00\",\"0.00\"]', '[[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"],[\"\",\"N\\/A\",\"0\",\"0\"]]', 0),
